<https://w3id.org/lca#> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://w3id.org/lca#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/contributor> <http://www.semanticweb.org/20180031/ontologies/2026/3/untitled-ontology-42#Martin_Röck> .
<https://w3id.org/lca#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> <http://www.semanticweb.org/20180031/ontologies/2026/3/untitled-ontology-42#Julia_Kaltenegger> .
<https://w3id.org/lca#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The Life Cycle Assessment ontology assignes Life Cycle Inventories to construction materials. The Life Cycle Inventory is discussed and outlines the required input and output for Life Cycle Assessment calculations." .
<https://w3id.org/lca#> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Life Cycle Assessment Ontology for building material performance" .
